snippet.title: Gautam Adani vs Hindenburg Report | Explained by Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
A few days back, Hindenburg released a report on Adani Group alleging that the group is involved in stock manipulation and accounting fraud, which not only led to Adani's big loss but also a huge deviation in the stock market. This sparked a big discussion and debate - is the Hindenburg report really true, or are there any personal gains involved in this situation? What was Adani's response to these allegations? Watch this video by Dhruv Rathee to find out as he deep dives into the history of Hindenburg to explain the current situation.

Tere Bin Episode 12 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 2nd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Roohe nee akalum munbuppane kandu marikkenam.
Allekil ummantte koode marikkenam.
Roohe nee piriyum munbuppane kandu marikkenam.
Vidhiyundel uppantte koode madagenam.
Ee mannil thunanigal pakaliravil punjagal...
Cheru novum ariyunnor.
Nira sneham pakarunnor.
Vanathil keezhe eni ennennum thudarenam...
     (Roohe..)

Thalarathe thakarathe duniyavil thanalayi ee ummantte nizhalayi ennum njanille.
Cherukudilil padavukalil mizhi edarathoru thiriyayi enn varavennum kaakkanoru nizhalayi neeyille.
Niramazhayil eriveyilil oru kudayay njanille.
Oru karuthal kadalakan ennuppa koottunde.
Niraravil nilav pozhinjath poloru sneham pakarunne.
Kalichiriyil kadha parayan  ennumma koodunde.
Kadhanathil karamekan ennuppa koottunde.
     (Roohe...)

Kaalathin oolethil ozhukunne cheruvanchi.
Athinerathii snehathin thuzhayayi njanunde.
Oru kattil ulayathe oru thirayil thakarathe ee janmathil kadavil thunayakanivanundo.
Oru theeyayi anayunnor ee maanava janmagal.
Oru theeyum pozhiyathe pakarami snehagal.
Udayorith ummayuppayum ulakiluyiril swasagal.
Oru puzhathan thelineeram ee sneham pakaramo.
Oru kadalin alapole ee sneham pakaramo.

snippet.title: BARREL COOKING | 3 Full Goat Cooking In Big Barrel | Whole Lamb Grill Recipe Cooking In Village
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook Three whole lambs in big barrels. We first marinated the lambs with traditional hand-ground masala. Then we cover it with the barrel. Finally, we made a fire around it. 
Normally mutton grill recipe is made with direct heat, but today, we pass the heat to the inside of the barrel to grill the full goat.

snippet.title: (Ep 03) @vikasdivyakirti सर ने इतनी पर्सनल बातें कहीं शेयर नहीं की | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Vikas जी की तरह सही Skills, मेहनत, जज़्बे और जुनून के साथ करें अपना हर सपना सच:https://joshskills.app.link/STwtRrQ41wb

Josh Talks brings you a series in which we will know about Dr.Vikas Divyakirti’s professional and personal lifestyle. Along with this, we will know what are his thoughts regarding UPSC Exam preparation and what his life inspirations have been.

This is Episode 03 of this series in which Dr. Vikas Divyakirti will discuss: 

1. Why he did not take himself seriously?
2. Does Vikas Divyakirti become successful by chance?
3. Which of being practical or emotional is a better choice?

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti is an IAS Trainer, Author, and Lecturer. He is the founder of Drishti IAS Coaching Classes, a UPSC Coaching Institute in Delhi. He was born in Haryana. He has done MA in Hindi literature from Delhi University. We must have heard him taking UPSC Mock Interview on Drishti IAS. From children to old people, they all are fans of his words. Many people put Dr. Vikas Divyakirti's Motivational Shorts and Videos on their Status. He also has a YouTube channel named Vikas Divyakirti. 

जोश Talks लाया है एक ऐसी सिरीज़ जिसमें हम जानेंगे Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की Professional और Personal Lifestyle के बारे में. साथ ही जानेंगे कि इनके UPSC Exam Preparation को लेकर क्या विचार हैं और इनकी क्या Life Inspirations रही हैं.

ये इस सिरीज़ का Episode 03 है जिसमें Dr. Vikas Divyakirti निम्नलिखित सवालों पर चर्चा करेंगे -

1. Vikas Divyakirti Sir खुद को Seriosly क्यूं नहीं लेते? 
2. क्या Vikas sir की success के पीछे तुक्के हैं?
3. Practical और Emotional होने में से क्या सही है?

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी IAS Trainer, Author और lecturer हैं. Drishti IAS Coaching Classes जो कि Delhi में एक UPSC Coaching Institute है, ये उसके Founder हैं. इनका जन्म Haryana में हुआ. इन्होंने Delhi University से Hindi literature में MA किया है. हुमनें इनको Drishti IAS पर UPSC Mock Interview लेते हुए सुना होगा. बच्चे से लेकर बूढ़े तक इनकी बातों के Fan हैं. कईं लोग Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की Motivational Shorts और Videos अपने Status पर लागते हैं. इनका एक YouTube channel भी है जिसका नाम है Vikas Divyakirti. 

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की ये Motivational Speech देख कर हमें Successful बनने का मार्गदर्शन और हौसला मिलेगा. 

#JoshTalksHindi #DrVikasDivyakirtiJoshTalks #DrVikasDivyakirti #vikasdivyakirtisir #vikasdivyakirti #vikasdivyakirtimotivation #vikasdivyakirtibiography #drvikasdivyakirti

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

► जोश Talks Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JoshTalksHindi​ 
► जोश Talks Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/JoshTalksHi...

Viewers are requested to use their own discretion while viewing the content and focus on the entirety of the story rather than finding inferences in its parts. Josh Talks by any means, does not further or amplify any specific ideology or propaganda.

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: "എന്റെ വീട്ടിൽ ഞാൻ SAFE അല്ലായിരുന്നു!" | @GLAMYGANGA | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
തന്റെ സ്വപ്‌നങ്ങൾ എല്ലാം തന്റെ കണ്മുന്നിൽ തകർന്നു വീഴുന്ന അവസ്ഥ ഒന്ന് ആലോചിച്ചു നോക്കൂ, ഇതു പോലെ ആയിരം സ്വപ്നങ്ങൾ ആയാണ് ഗംഗ  തന്റെ  ജീവിതത്തിലേക്ക് കടക്കുന്നത്. എന്നാൽ തന്റെ സ്വപ്ങ്ങൾ അല്ല യാഥാർഥ്യം എന്നു മനസിലാക്കിയപ്പോൾ ആരെ പോലെയും തളർന്നു പോയെങ്കിലും വീണു പോകാൻ ഗംഗ തയ്യാറായില്ലായിരുന്നു .കുട്ടികാലം മുതൽ താൻ അനുഭവിച്ച trauma ക്കു ഒരു അവസാനം ആയാണ് ഗംഗ തന്റെ യു ട്യൂബ് യാത്ര ആരഭിക്കുന്നത്. തന്നെ തളർത്താൻ കെല്പുള്ള പല അവസരങ്ങളും ജീവിതത്തിലൂടെ കടന്നു പോയിട്ടും തളരാതെ നിന്ന് തനിക്കു വേണ്ടി സമയം കൊടുത്തു, താൻ തോൽക്കില്ല എന്ന ഉറച്ച തീരുമാനത്തിൽ തുടങ്ങിയ യാത്ര ഇന്ന് നമ്മോടൊപ്പം ജോഷ് talks വരെ എത്തി നിൽക്കുകയാണ്. ഗംഗയുടെ കഥ നമ്മുടെ പലരുടേയും കഥ ആകാം, ഒന്നും ഒന്നിനും ഒരു അവസാനമല്ല മറിച്ചു തന്നെ , തന്നെ തെളിയിക്കാൻ ഉള്ള അവസരണം ആണ് എന്നു തീരുമാനത്തിൽ മുന്നോട്ടു പോകാൻ ഈ കഥ നിങ്ങളുടെ തീർച്ചയായും സഹായിക്കും.

Think about the situation where all her dreams are crumbling before her eyes, Ganga enters her life as a thousand dreams like this. But when she realized that her dreams were not reality, Ganga was not ready to give up even though she was tired like anyone else. Even though many opportunities have passed through her life that could have weakened him, she did not get tired and took time for herself, and the journey that started with a firm decision that's she will not lose has reached Josh talks with us today. This story will definitely help you to decide that the story of Ganga can be the story of many of us, nothing is the end of anything, but it is an opportunity to prove yourself.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalis. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ജോഷ് Talks ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രേരണാത്മകമായ കഥകൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും അവയെ പങ്കുവെക്കാൻ ഒരു വേദി നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നു. വിവിധ പശ്ചാത്തലങ്ങളിൽ നിന്നുള്ള അനുഭവസ്ഥർ അവരുടെ സംഘർഷഭരിത കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഒരു സമ്മേളനമായി തുടങ്ങിയ ജോഷ് Talks, നിലവിൽ 9 ഭാഷകളിൽ കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

localized.description:
തന്റെ സ്വപ്‌നങ്ങൾ എല്ലാം തന്റെ കണ്മുന്നിൽ തകർന്നു വീഴുന്ന അവസ്ഥ ഒന്ന് ആലോചിച്ചു നോക്കൂ, ഇതു പോലെ ആയിരം സ്വപ്നങ്ങൾ ആയാണ് ഗംഗ  തന്റെ  ജീവിതത്തിലേക്ക് കടക്കുന്നത്. എന്നാൽ തന്റെ സ്വപ്ങ്ങൾ അല്ല യാഥാർഥ്യം എന്നു മനസിലാക്കിയപ്പോൾ ആരെ പോലെയും തളർന്നു പോയെങ്കിലും വീണു പോകാൻ ഗംഗ തയ്യാറായില്ലായിരുന്നു .കുട്ടികാലം മുതൽ താൻ അനുഭവിച്ച trauma ക്കു ഒരു അവസാനം ആയാണ് ഗംഗ തന്റെ യു ട്യൂബ് യാത്ര ആരഭിക്കുന്നത്. തന്നെ തളർത്താൻ കെല്പുള്ള പല അവസരങ്ങളും ജീവിതത്തിലൂടെ കടന്നു പോയിട്ടും തളരാതെ നിന്ന് തനിക്കു വേണ്ടി സമയം കൊടുത്തു, താൻ തോൽക്കില്ല എന്ന ഉറച്ച തീരുമാനത്തിൽ തുടങ്ങിയ യാത്ര ഇന്ന് നമ്മോടൊപ്പം ജോഷ് talks വരെ എത്തി നിൽക്കുകയാണ്. ഗംഗയുടെ കഥ നമ്മുടെ പലരുടേയും കഥ ആകാം, ഒന്നും ഒന്നിനും ഒരു അവസാനമല്ല മറിച്ചു തന്നെ , തന്നെ തെളിയിക്കാൻ ഉള്ള അവസരണം ആണ് എന്നു തീരുമാനത്തിൽ മുന്നോട്ടു പോകാൻ ഈ കഥ നിങ്ങളുടെ തീർച്ചയായും സഹായിക്കും.

Think about the situation where all her dreams are crumbling before her eyes, Ganga enters her life as a thousand dreams like this. But when she realized that her dreams were not reality, Ganga was not ready to give up even though she was tired like anyone else. Even though many opportunities have passed through her life that could have weakened him, she did not get tired and took time for herself, and the journey that started with a firm decision that's she will not lose has reached Josh talks with us today. This story will definitely help you to decide that the story of Ganga can be the story of many of us, nothing is the end of anything, but it is an opportunity to prove yourself.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalis. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ജോഷ് Talks ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രേരണാത്മകമായ കഥകൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും അവയെ പങ്കുവെക്കാൻ ഒരു വേദി നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നു. വിവിധ പശ്ചാത്തലങ്ങളിൽ നിന്നുള്ള അനുഭവസ്ഥർ അവരുടെ സംഘർഷഭരിത കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഒരു സമ്മേളനമായി തുടങ്ങിയ ജോഷ് Talks, നിലവിൽ 9 ഭാഷകളിൽ കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.

snippet.title: INDIAN BUDGET EXPLAINED IN 10 MINUTES | Budget 2023 explained | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain the process in which the Union Budget is made and take a look at some of the top spends in the 2023 Union Budget

The Budget is an important document because it signifies the direction that the Government wants to take. It gives a chance to the people to see which ministry takes up most of the resources and understand how much money the Government makes and where they spend it. It is time all of us analyze the data and ask the Government the right questions. 

This video will help you demystify the Budget process and understand the basics of this event

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

#budget2023 #finance #economy 

Stay ahead of the game with our exclusive coverage of the Indian Budget 2023. Our in-depth analysis breaks down the latest fiscal policies, economic indicators and their impact on citizens and businesses. Get a complete rundown of government spending and revenue, including allocation for key sectors such as education, health, infrastructure, and more. With expert insights and easy to understand explanations, our video is the go-to source for staying informed on the Indian Budget 2023. Watch now to stay ahead of the curve and make informed decisions.

snippet.title: ఈ వీడియో చూస్తే విశ్వనాధ్ గారి గొప్పతనం తెలుస్తుంది ..Chiru,Venky,Trivikram,RGV About K.Vishwanath
snippet.description:
Filmmaker-actor K Viswanath passed away in Hyderabad on Thursday. In a career spanning six decades,  K Viswanath visualized themes like Telugu culture, Telugu Music, the caste system, untouchability, gender discrimination, dowry and socio-economic challenges in his movies. Chelleli Kapuram, Kalam Marindi, Sarada, O Seeta Katha Jeevana Jyothi, Siri Siri Muvva, Sankarabharanam, Saptapadi, Sagara Sangamamm, Swathi Muthyam, Sruthilayalu, Swarnakamalam, Sutradharulu, Aapadbhandhuvudu, Swati Kiranam, Subha Sankalpam, Swarabhishekam, Sargam, Kaamchor, Shubh Kaamna, Eeshwar and Dhanwaan are few of his acclaimed films. 

We must noted,  K Viswanath movie Swathi Muthyam was picked as India’s official entry for the Oscars in 1986. He worked with Kamal Haasan, Jayaprada, Rishi Kapoor, Anil Kapoor, Vanisri and Chiranjeevi among others.

snippet.description:
Subscribe To Shemaroo Movie in Parts: https://www.youtube.com/user/shemaroopremiumfilms?sub_confirmation=1

Ravi is forced to work as a servant for a Thaku . During the village elections, Ravi decides to take a stand by running against the wealthy tyrant But the landowner ups the ante with an unusual wager, offering his daughter as the prize.

Directed by K. Bapaiah
Written by Kader Khan (dialogues)
Screenplay by Amar Shamji
Story by Malliyam Rajagopal
Produced by A. KRishnamurthi
Starring - Mithun Chakraborty, Amrita Singh

Edited by Waman Bhonsle, Gurudutt Shirali
Music by Laxmikant-Pyarelal

कादर खान द्वारा लिखित (संवाद)
पटकथा अमर शामजी
मालियम राजगोपाल की कहानी

snippet.title: தைப்பூசம் 2023 -  தீய சக்தி, நவக்கிரக தோஷங்கள், பகை நீங்க முருகனை வழிபடும் முறை | Thaipusam 2023
snippet.description:
தைப்பூச தினத்தில் முருகனை வழிபடும் முறை, செய்ய வேண்டிய நெய்வேத்தியம், நேரம், படிக்க வேண்டிய பதிகங்கள் என அனைத்து தகவல்களையும் இந்தப் பதிவில் திருமதி. தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி அம்மா அவர்கள் அளித்துள்ளார். 

வீட்டில் வேல் வழிபாடு செய்யும் முறை | "VEL" Worship method at Home explained by Desa Mangayarkarasi
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eLhE25OaEj8

நாளென் செயும்வினை தானென் செயுமெனை நாடிவந்த
கோளென் செயுங்கொடுங் கூற்றென் செயுங்கும ரேசரிரு
தாளுஞ் சிலம்புஞ் சதங்கையும் தண்டையுஞ் சண்முகமுந்
தோளுங் கடம்பு மெனக்குமுன் னேவந்து தோன்றிடினே

பாடல் 1:
அப்பா நான் வேண்டுதல் கேட்டருள் புரிதல் வேண்டும்
ஆருயிர்கட்கெல்லாம் நான் அன்பு செயல் வேண்டும்
எப்பாரும் எப்பதமும் எங்கணும் நான் சென்றே
எந்தை நினதருட் புகழை இயம்பிடல் வேண்டும்
செப்பாத மேல்நிலைமேல் சுத்த சிவ மார்க்கம்
திகழ்ந்தோங்க அருட்சோதி செலுத்தியிடல் வேண்டும்
தப்பேது நான்செயினும் நீ பொறுத்தல் வேண்டும்
தலைவா நினைப் பிரியாத நிலைமையும் வேண்டுவனே.

பாடல் 2:
ஒருமையுடன் நினது திரு மலரடி நினைக்கின்ற
உத்தமர்தம் உறவுவேண்டும்
உள் ஒன்று வைத்துப் புறம்பொன்று பேசுவார்
உறவு கலவாமை வேண்டும்
பெருமைபெறு நினதுபுகழ் பேசவேண் டும் பொய்மை
பேசாதிருக்கவேண்டும்
பெருநெறி பிடித்தொழுக வேண்டும் மதமான பேய்
பிடியாதிருக்கவேண்டும்
மருவுபெண் ஆசையை மறக்கவே வேண்டும் உனை
மறவாதிருக்கவேண்டும்
மதிவேண்டும்  நின் கருணை நிதி வேண்டும்  நோயற்ற
வாழ்வில் நான் வாழவேண்டும்
தருமமிகு சென்னையில் கந்தகோட் டத்துள் வளர்
தலம் ஓங்கு கந்தவேளே
தண்முகத் துய்யமணி  உண்முகச் சைவமணி
சண்முகத் தெய்வமணியே.

பாடல் 3
அன்பெனும் பிடியுள் அகப்படும் மலையே
அன்பெனும் குடில்புகும் அரசே
அன்பெனும் வலைக்குட் படுபரம் பொருளே
அன்பெனும் கரத்தமர் அமுதே
அன்பெனும் கடத்துள் அடங்கிடும் கடலே
அன்பெனும் உயிர்ஒளிர் அறிவே
அன்பெனும் அணுவுள் ளமைந்தபே ரொளியே
அன்புரு வாம்பர சிவமே.

பாடல் 4
எத்துணையும் பேதமுறாது எவ்வுயிரும்
⁠தம் உயிர்போல் எண்ணி உள்ளே
ஒத்துரிமை யுடையவராய் உவக்கின்றார்
⁠யாவர் அவர் உளந்தான் சுத்த
சித்துருவாய் எம் பெருமான் நடம்புரியும்
⁠இடம் என நான் தெரிந்தேன் அந்த
வித்தகர்தம் அடிக்கேவல் புரிந்திட என்
⁠சிந்தை மிக விழைந்த தாலோ.

அன்பெனும் உயிர்ஒளிர் அறிவே
அன்பெனும் அணுவுள் ளமைந்தபே ரொளியே
அன்புரு வாம்பர சிவமே.

பாடல் 4
எத்துணையும் பேதமுறாது எவ்வுயிரும்
⁠தம் உயிர்போல் எண்ணி உள்ளே
ஒத்துரிமை யுடையவராய் உவக்கின்றார்
⁠யாவர் அவர் உளந்தான் சுத்த
சித்துருவாய் எம் பெருமான் நடம்புரியும்
⁠இடம் என நான் தெரிந்தேன் அந்த
வித்தகர்தம் அடிக்கேவல் புரிந்திட என்
⁠சிந்தை மிக விழைந்த தாலோ.

snippet.description:
Hey Guys ,

This Video has everything that happens in a School Exams , Indian Schools and Indian Colleges during this Valentines week . The most relatable and Funny Video .  You will be filled with nostalgia for your school days and College days . 
Scenarios like bunking college during valentine week , college friend helping in proposing girlfriend cause of propose day , new college couples celebrating rose day , teddy day , hug day , kiss day , valentines day . exam answersheet distribution day , college teachers and their horror of facing them personally in staff room . Last Exam and exciting of going out with friends after exam and playing paint ball , going mall eating in the food court getting lot of pictures . getting ready especially to impress the college crush . College Exams and not worrying about failing any exam , and are prepared to give paper back in next semester . Back agyi , back logs their fees of reappearing in the exams . Indian mom worried about the girl's fashion in college and not thinking about exam prep , revision , pens , cardboard and just carriying metro card and single pen . Students wishing they get a nice invigilator but gets Strict invigilator , gets caught cheating using phone , other friends also leaving examination hall to support their friendship . Planning in Advance group studies . Indian parents just wishing their children becomes doctor , engineer , or gets good placement . The pressure a day before exam . studying full day . College freinds calling and discussing how much syllabus they've completed , chatterbox friends passing time on call , teaching boyfriend on call whole night , puting multiple alarms to wake up early morning to do revision . mom feeding us almonds , badam , coffee , milk , chawan prash . Playing hide n seek in chilhood , mummy scolding to study for exams coming , checking datesheet , tution teacher focusing on toppers . Moms giving lecture on exam results . Exam Day , types of students during exams , praying To God to help pass the exam , question paper out of syllabus, students freaking out , teacher allowing them to cheat , backbenchers trying to copy from toppers answer sheets , some monitors crying for more time , coming overprepared with lots of Pens , wearing home clothes that , fancy dress to school on birthday, getting birthday bumps and distributing toffee treats to whole class room and teachers in the staff room but giving an extra to toffee to our best friend, girls Fight due fountain Pen ink leak  , choosing subject Sanskrit, hindi , french , calling Mam mummy by mistake , home science class , art n craft teacher teaching stocking flowers , supw class , Strict Teacher scolding class taking test of digestive System, That PTM day, sharing lunch boxes in classroom with friends, bringing rajma Chawal and treating class teacher , every Indian mom scolding cause of bad result , other aunties distributing laddoo ,  Students of the class paying for those School Photographs , Eating in recess with school friends from school canteen , Getting punished by Mam cause of the her fav class monitor student , completing holiday homework those, chart papers, models , summer vacation , that tuition life , and much more .. Girls School. The most relatable and Funny Video . Scenarios like Secretly Bringing Phone in School, Fainting In Assembly, a girl spreading rumours, a teacher's Pet in Class , wearing wrong uniform on the wrong day, Crush on Male Teacher, many more .. snippet.title: एक वेश्या ने कोठे को गिरवी रख कर अपने यार को छुड़वाया | सनी देओल एक्शन मुवी | तब्बू की मुवी
snippet.description:
Karan, a dreaded gangster, falls in love with Kajal, the daughter of his nemesis Prof. Siddharth. After initial hesitation Kajal reciprocates Karans advances and tries to reform him with her love. However, Prof. Siddharth forces Kajal to marry Raju, the son of his childhood friend, Ramakanth. Thus, Karan returns to his violent old days after suffering the heartbreak. Watch to know what transpires when Karan finds out that Raju is his next target. Will Karan kill Raju or stand guard for him against the odds?Watch to know more.  Watch to know more.  

Movie - Jeet (1996)
StarCast - Salman Khan, Sunny Deol, Karishma Kapoor, Tabu, Amrish Puri, Alok Nath
Director - Raj Kanwar
Producer - Sajid Nadiadwala
Cinematography - A. Muthu
Editor - Harmeet Singh
Music Director - Nadeem-Shravan

#sunnydeolmovies #sunnydeolactionscene #karishmakapoor 

खूंखार गैंगस्टर करण को काजल से प्यार हो जाता है, जो उसके विरोधी प्रोफेसर सिद्धार्थ की बेटी है। शुरुआती झिझक के बाद काजल करण की बातों का जवाब देती है और अपने प्यार से उसे सुधारने की कोशिश करती है। हालाँकि, प्रो सिद्धार्थ काजल को अपने बचपन के दोस्त रमाकांत के बेटे राजू से शादी करने के लिए मजबूर करते हैं। इस प्रकार, दिल टूटने के बाद करण अपने हिंसक पुराने दिनों में लौट आता है। यह जानने के लिए देखें कि क्या होता है जब करण को पता चलता है कि राजू उसका अगला निशाना है। क्या करण राजू को मार डालेगा या बाधाओं से उसकी रक्षा करेगा?अधिक जानने के लिए देखें। अधिक जानने के लिए देखें।

मूवी - जीत (1996)
स्टार कास्ट - सलमान खान, सनी देओल, करिश्मा कपूर, तब्बू, अमरीश पुरी, आलोक नाथ

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 13 Teaser - 2nd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 13 Teaser - 2nd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

#wahajali

snippet.title: कम तेल में बना ऐसा नाश्ता जो पहले कभी ना आपने देखा होगा ना कभी खाया होगा | Healthy Breakfast Recipe
snippet.description:
कम तेल में बना ऐसा नाश्ता जो पहले कभी ना आपने देखा होगा ना कभी खाया होगा | Healthy Breakfast Recipe

#HealthyBreakfast#VegOmelet#NirmlaNehraRecipes

Ingredients:-
Raw Rice-1 cup
Carrot-1 medium size
Tomato-1 small size
Onion-1 medium size 
Capsicum-1 medium size 
Chopped Cabbage-1/4 cup
Potato-1 medium size 
Green Chilli-1-2
Ginger-1 inch
Mustard Seeds-1 tsp
Cumin Seeds-1/2 tsp
Red Chilli Flakes-1 tsp
Sesame Seeds-1 tsp
Curry Leaves-10-12
Salt-to taste
Oil/Ghee-1-2 tsp+for greasing 
Coriander Leaves

Mujhe Pyaar Hua Tha; What You Want & What Your Destiny Wants

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3685 - 3 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3685: Surprise Gift For Taarak
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak is worried because his boss is paying a visit to his place. Taarak's boss wants to meet Badey Guruji after his prediction about the contract. Bapuji has gone for a walk in the park and Sodhi and Taarak are trying to stop him so that Bapuji doesn't come across Taarak's boss. When Boss finally reaches Gokuldham Taarak very cautiously takes him inside his house. The boss puts a condition before Taarak that he will sponsor the Europe trip only if he gets to meet the Badey Guruji. What will Taarak do now? Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3685, 3 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000208213

snippet.title: Women Task Force | Undercover Officer Purvi Gets Hit By The Dangerous Biker Gang | CID | 31 Jan 2023
snippet.description:
There is big planning going on in a stunt bikers' group regarding an event named Mission ABG: JO that is supposed to be held soon. They are planning to commit a bank robbery. The CID team starts catching the members of the group one by one and decodes the secret behind the Mission ABG: JO. Watch the full episode to find out how the CID team cuts through the chase.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1206
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #livcrime #सीआईडी #NewCID #LatestCID #CID2023

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIW-oBRmsADGpsfuNkU81C

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. http://supr.cl/ThisArmy

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Shaakuntalam Movie also in 3D, Written & Directed by Gunasekhar, Presented by Dil Raju under Sri Venkateswara Creations in collaboration with Gunaa Teamworks, Produced by Neelima Guna.

The massively mounted film Shaakuntalam based on internationally acclaimed Kalidasa’s Sanskrit play ‘Abhijnana Shakuntalam’ is all set to release in Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam & Kannada.  The story of Shaakuntalam revolves around the epic love story of Shakuntala and King Dushyant from Mahabharata, portrayed by Samantha and Dev Mohan.

The film is helmed by supremely proficient, Director Gunasekhar and marks a whimsical tale of love set in the Kashyapa Kanumalu (Kashmir), the grandeur and splendour of Dushyant’s Puru Dynasty making the film extremely exceptional.

*About* 
------------

                 Judwa behene Divya aur Drishti ko apne janam se mila hai shakti ka vardaan. Drishti bhavishya kaal ko dekh sakti hai aur Divya ussey badal sakti hai. Inke mata pita ne apni jaan ka balidaan dekar bachaya dono beheno ko par bichad gaye bachpan mai Divya aur Drishti. Alag alag parivaaron mai pale bade par ek doosre ko dhundhte rahe. 
Ek kaali shakti - Pishaachini haasil karna chahti hai sarva shaktishali Kaal Vijay Ratna ko aur saalon se padi hai dono beheno ke peeche. Dobara mil hi jaati hai Divya aur Drishti. Ek saath milkar karti hai muqaabla Pishaachini ka aur karte hai waada ussey khatam karne ka.

snippet.title: Gautam Adani Explains Why Adani Enterprises FPO Was Withdrawn
snippet.description:
#gautamadani #FPOwithdrawal, #adanifpo 
After the stunning decision by the Adani Group to withdraw the ₹20,000-cr FPO of Adani Enterprises, an early morning statement was released by the group to explain this move. Chairman Gautam Adani takes the high moral ground and says the capital market strategy will be reviewed once the market stabilizes. He also reassures investors of the financial stability of the group.

snippet.title: Bihaan को है होली से नफ़रत! | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 612
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

On the occasion of Holi, Thapki tries to apply some colours on Bihaan but is shocked when he gets furious and stops her. Vasundhara reveals that Bihaan is traumatised by old memories and stays away from Holi celebrations. Shraddha and Sankar plan to get Bihaan out of his room to celebrate Holi before Thapki gets a chance to do so. Will they succeed?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3682 - Boss Ne Liya Guruji Ka Aashirvad?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

snippet.title: (Ep-2) UPSC Aspirants किसी भी हाल में @vikasdivyakirti की इन बातों को Miss मत करना👆|Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Vikas जी की तरह सही Skills, मेहनत, जज़्बे और जुनून के साथ करें अपना हर सपना सच: https://joshskills.app.link/YtNYUGvmVwb

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti की ज़िंदगी बदल देने वाली बातें (Full Playlist🔥) :- 
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL1D6nWQpbEZf2bV4kpEOmee0aPcAqol19

Josh Talks brings you a series in which we will know about Dr.Vikas Divyakirti’s professional and personal lifestyle. Along with this, we will know what are his thoughts regarding UPSC Exam preparation and what his life inspirations have been.

This is Episode 02 of this series in which Dr. Vikas Divyakirti will discuss the following questions -

1. What has been the importance of Hindi and English Mediums in UPSC Results?
2. Online or Offline Education for UPSC Preparation, which is better?
3. What is Vikas Divyakirti Sir's opinion about the affordable and expensive UPSC Institutes?

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti is an IAS Trainer, Author, and Lecturer. He is the founder of Drishti IAS Coaching Classes, a UPSC Coaching Institute in Delhi. He was born in Haryana. He has done MA in Hindi literature from Delhi University. We must have heard him taking UPSC Mock Interview on Drishti IAS. From children to old people, they all are fans of his words. Many people put Dr. Vikas Divyakirti's Motivational Shorts and Videos on their Status. He also has a YouTube channel named Vikas Divyakirti. 

जोश Talks लाया है एक ऐसी सिरीज़ जिसमें हम जानेंगे Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की Professional और Personal Lifestyle के बारे में. साथ ही जानेंगे कि इनके UPSC Exam Preparation को लेकर क्या विचार हैं और इनकी क्या Life Inspirations रही हैं.

ये इस सिरीज़ का Episode 02 है जिसमें Dr. Vikas Divyakirti निम्नलिखित सवालों पर चर्चा करेंगे -

1. UPSC के Result में Hindi और English Medium का क्या महत्व रहा है? 
2. UPSC Preparation के लिए Online या Offline Education, क्या बेहतर है?
3. Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की Affordable और Expensive UPSC Institute को लेकर क्या राय है?

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी IAS Trainer, Author और lecturer हैं. Drishti IAS Coaching Classes जो कि Delhi में एक UPSC Coaching Institute है, ये उसके Founder हैं. इनका जन्म Haryana में हुआ. इन्होंने Delhi University से Hindi literature में MA किया है. हुमनें इनको Drishti IAS पर UPSC Mock Interview लेते हुए सुना होगा. बच्चे से लेकर बूढ़े तक इनकी बातों के Fan हैं. कईं लोग Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की Motivational Shorts और Videos अपने Status पर लागते हैं. इनका एक YouTube channel भी है जिसका नाम है Vikas Divyakirti. 

Dr. Vikas Divyakirti जी की ये Motivational Speech देख कर हमें Successful बनने का मार्गदर्शन और हौसला मिलेगा. 

#JoshTalksHindi #DrVikasDivyakirtiJoshTalks #DrVikasDivyakirti #vikasdivyakirtisir #vikasdivyakirti #vikasdivyakirtimotivation #vikasdivyakirtibiography #drvikasdivyakirti

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

► जोश Talks Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/JoshTalksHi...

snippet.title: 10 साल पहले के Incident को कैसे Expose करेगी CID? | CID | A Planned Conspiracy |सीआईडी | 30 Jan 2023
snippet.description:
Ketan is an architect. He gets some bullets on his site. Whose information he gives to Team CID. Daya goes to the crime scene and investigates. He goes to the nearby forests to get more information about this case. An elderly person there tells about a farmhouse where some bullets were fired 10 years ago. What happened 10 years ago in that farmhouse? How will Daya and Team CID solve the case? Watch the full episode to know. 

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi

snippet.title: NEW! Maddam Sir - Ep 728 - 3 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 728: Chor Reunion Party
--------------------------------------------
Naina informs Maddam Sir that she has decided to clear Cherry's name. When questioned, Naina informs Haseena that she has struck a deal with Cherry in exchange for Haseena's release from the false accusation. Later, Naina and Billu attend a Chor reunion party to learn more about Cherry. Karishma Singh, on the other hand, interrogates some women with criminal records in order to identify the person for whom Maddam Sir fell into this trap. Stay tuned for more information!

Show Name – Maddam Sir
Star Cast –  Gulki Joshi, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Episode No – 728, 3 Feb 2023
Produced By –  Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir  #मैड्डमसर #SAB

Click here to Subscribe to SAB TV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sabtv?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the circumstances add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences add to the drama madam and comedy.

Dekhiye kaise saari kadvi Sachchaaiyon se joojhte huye, donon ka rishta aage baddhta hai.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3684 - 2 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3684: Boss Ka Surprise
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha tries to sneak out and watch the television when Bapuji tells him to stay in his room and not watch late-night television, but Champaklal drags him back to his room. The following morning, Taarak gets a call from his boss saying that he is on the way and would be dropping by his house. Taarak is horrified since he cannot afford for Bapuji and his boss to confront each other since Bapuji is the "Bade Guruji" in his boss's eyes. Can Taarak keep his falsehoods a secret? Remain tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3684, 2 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

The Lallantop Show - 2 February, 2023:
The Adani Group, on 01 February decided to call off the Follow-on Public Offer (FPO) of equity shares aggregating up to Rs 20,000 crore of face value Rs 1 each on a partly paid-up basis, which was fully subscribed. Shares of Adani Group companies continued their downward spiral on the stock market on 02 February, even as the conglomerate’s billionaire owner Gautam Adani released a video statement to calm investors. In The Lallantop Show, we have once again talked about the Adani Group. We have tried to understand whether there is really something wrong going on in the Adani Group or whether any conspiracy has been hatched against this group.

snippet.title: जया एकादशी व्रत कथा | jaya ekadashi ki katha | ekadashi vrat katha | जया एकादशी की कहानी
snippet.description:
जया एकादशी व्रत कथा | jaya ekadashi ki katha | ekadashi vrat katha | जया एकादशी की कहानी

नमस्कार दोस्तों, आज  01 फरवरी 2023 को जया एकादशी के अवसर पर मैं आप सभी के समक्ष माघ शुक्ल पक्ष की जया एकादशी की कथा प्रस्तुत कर रही हूं। आइए शुरू करते हैं जया एकादशी की कथा पूजा विधि  महत्त्व 

धर्मराज युधिष्ठिर बोले - हे भगवन्! आप कृपा करके माघ शुक्ल एकादशी का वर्णन कीजिए। इसका क्या नाम है, इसके व्रत की क्या विधि है और इसमें कौन से देवता का पूजन किया जाता है?
श्रीकृष्ण कहने लगे कि हे राजन्! इस एकादशी का नाम 'जया एकादशी' है। इसका व्रत करने से मनुष्य भूत, पिशाच आदि योनियों से मुक्त हो जाता है, ब्रह्महत्या आदि पापों से छूट कर मोक्ष को प्राप्त होता है। इस व्रत के प्रताप से व्‍यक्ति के सभी पापों का नाश होता है और घर में सुख-संपत्ति आती है. इस व्रत को विधिपूर्वक करना चाहिए।इसका व्रत करने पर मनुष्यों को कभी प्रेतयोनि में नहीं जाना पड़ता । जो लोग एकादशी का व्रत नहीं कर पाते हैं वह भी आज के दिन विष्णु भगवान की पूजा करके जया एकादशी की कथा को सुनें,विष्णु जी के नामों को मन ही मन पाठ करें और जरुरतमंदों की सहायता करें तो इससे भी पुण्य की प्राप्ति कर सकते हैं ।
अब मैं आपको जया एकादशी के महात्म्य की एक कथा सुनाता हूँ।
Hello friends, today, on the occasion of Jaya Ekadashi on 01 February 2023, I am presenting to you all the story of Jaya Ekadashi of Magh Shukla Paksha. Let's start the story of Jaya Ekadashi, story of worship, and importance

Dharmaraja Yudhishthira said - O God! Kindly describe Magh Shukla Ekadashi. What is its name, what is the method of its fast and which deity is worshiped in it?
Shri Krishna started saying that O Rajan! The name of this Ekadashi is 'Jaya Ekadashi'. By observing this, a person is freed from the vagaries of ghosts, vampires etc., attains salvation by getting rid of sins etc. All the sins of a person are destroyed by the brilliance of this fast and there is happiness and wealth in the house. This fast should be done in a systematic way. Humans never have to go to the haunted world after fasting it. Those who are not able to observe Ekadashi fast, also listen to the story of Jaya Ekadashi by worshiping Lord Vishnu on this day, recite the names of Vishnu ji by heart and help the needy, then you can also achieve virtue by this .
Now let me tell you a story of the great significance of Jaya Ekadashi.

#jayaekadashivratkatha   #जयाएकादशी #ekadashivrat
#jayaekadashivratkatha

Dabde nayi dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne


Maade jo time ch chad gaye kise nal harkh nayi koi 
Koi sanu ki samje painda hun fark ni koi 
Koi lakh kar jaye maada mathe kade vatt ni paya 
Pandita nu future de layi main nayi kade hath dikhaya 
Sach ni koi hoya aisa jo akhan ne biyan ni kareya 
Hoya ni saadh koi aisa rabb da jine dhayan ni dhareya 
Jinna vich uddeya firda saadh pune diya loran ne 
Dabde nayi dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne


Dheethan nal dheeth bade aa aunde kise guage ch haini 
Kimat meri puch ona ton jina di main range ch haini 
Chadar ton bahar kade vi nek na pair pasare 
Bolan di lod ni sanu paundi aa chupp khilare 
Sade te asar nayi kareya oh allarhan diyaan toran ne 
Vekhe kayi khunje laate jhanjar deya shoran ne 
Allarha impress karan layi na kaddiya kade tohra ne 
Dabde ni dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne

snippet.title: PLAYGROUND 2 AUCTION | @CarryMinati @triggeredinsaan, Scout, Ashish & Harsh Beniwal
snippet.description:
Playground is back! CarryMinati, Triggered Insaan, Ashish, ScoutOP & Harsh are trying to find the best contestants for the real money auction & pick them for their teams for the season starting 30th January streaming LIVE on YT & on Amazon miniTV! 

Voting lines for Super Subs open on Rumble, closes at 4:30 PM on 30th January. Vote here https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.robosoft.playverseStage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*Auction rules*
• 40 contestants
• Only 28 will remain post auction
• 20 players, selected through bidding, will go directly into teams 
• 8 players will go into super subs
 • Of this, 5 players will be selected by the 5 mentors
 • And 3 players will be selected through voting on Rumble
• Player mix for teams - 1 Pro-player, 1 international player, Min. 1 player from previous season, Min. 1 female player
• Every week two players will get eliminated and new players will be selected from supers subs 
• 25L purse of each mentor to bid for players
• If a mentor has invoked an RTM card for a player during the Tryouts, they have the Right to Match the final bid on that player during the auction
• Mentors can retain players from their last season team, retained players will not be put up for auction, 35% of purse amount will be retention fee for retained player
